# Helpful Crosshair

**1.21.11 -> 1.21.5** | Fabric

<hr>

Adds useful, quality of life, indicators ("hints") next to the crosshair!

Here's what they look like:

<img src="https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/7M5J9JvV/images/0c13126f5e0f1e79bb23117c7a9076de493177d5.jpeg" alt="Hint showing that the redstone level is 6" title="Hint showing that the redstone level is 6" width="300" />

<img src="https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/7M5J9JvV/images/eea1e2776a85a749ae44f8596f7fa3d6c628e653.jpeg" alt="Hint showing a wooden pickaxe cannot mine a deepslate redstone block" title="Hint showing a wooden pickaxe cannot mine a deepslate redstone block" width="300" />

<img src="https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/7M5J9JvV/images/d053d9826595531438fd16c7e1e1464a34a80c7b.jpeg" alt="Hint showing the player has leashed 3 cows" title="Hint showing the player has leashed 3 cows" width="300" />

<img src="https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/7M5J9JvV/images/7e2d06e85f084c7baba6875a5ca39f63b3e36fdc.jpeg" alt="Hint showing the player, who is holding a bow, will shoot tipped arrows and there are 33 arrows remaining" title="Hint showing the player, who is holding a bow, will shoot tipped arrows and there are 33 arrows remaining" width="300" />

<img src="https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/7M5J9JvV/images/9b4455eb492ed9486af92601a9eae2fc152b2950.jpeg" alt="Hint showing the equipped wooden pickaxe has 13 durability left" title="Hint showing the equipped wooden pickaxe has 13 durability left" width="300" />

<img src="https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/7M5J9JvV/images/666c548341e5509175dd116fa3d75de0902b75e5.jpeg" alt="Hint showing the carrot plant is 100% grown" title="Hint showing the carrot plant is 100% grown" width="300" />

&nbsp;

## Configuration

The `helpful_crosshair.config.json` file will be generated when you first load the game with the mod. You can enable/disable hints here!

Example _(last updated v0.1)_:

```
{
  "hints": [
    {
      "identifier": "incorrect_tool",
      "enabled": true
    },
    {
      "identifier": "tool_durability",
      "enabled": true
    },
    {
      "identifier": "arrow_count",
      "enabled": true
    },
    {
      "identifier": "redstone_level",
      "enabled": true
    },
    {
      "identifier": "leashed_mobs",
      "enabled": true
    },
    {
      "identifier": "crop_growth",
      "enabled": true
    }
  ]
}
```
